# VibeSafe Update Guide

## How to Update VibeSafe

Update VibeSafe by running the installation script from your project root:

```bash
bash <(curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lawrennd/vibesafe/main/scripts/install-minimal.sh)
```

VibeSafe follows the **Clean Installation Philosophy** - every installation is also a reinstallation.

